(laughing)

00:17:30.592 --> 00:17:33.561 position:35% line:89% align:start
(laughing)

00:17:33.595 --> 00:17:35.530 position:41% line:89% align:start
(grunt)

00:17:36.564 --> 00:17:37.798 position:41% line:89% align:start
An elk!

00:17:47.175 --> 00:17:50.111 position:24% line:89% align:start
(harpy screeching)

00:18:00.255 --> 00:18:02.524 position:35% line:89% align:start
