00:18:04.459 --> 00:18:07.395 position:24% line:89% align:start
(horses galloping)

00:18:29.518 --> 00:18:31.587 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:18:44.467 --> 00:18:46.502 position:19% line:89% align:start
- Let's make a promise.

00:18:46.535 --> 00:18:50.473 position:16% line:83% align:start
We won't let anyone spoil
the time we have left.

00:18:58.114 --> 00:18:59.682 position:33% line:89% align:start
- I love it!

00:18:59.715 --> 00:19:04.019 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm taking in the summer like
a bee gathering up nectar.

00:19:07.156 --> 00:19:11.560 position:16% line:83% align:start
Gathering it all together
in a big lump of summer

00:19:11.594 --> 00:19:13.362 position:19% line:89% align:start
to live on, to live on

00:19:14.597 --> 00:19:19.468 position:33% line:83% align:start
when it's not
summertime anymore.

00:19:24.541 --> 00:19:26.942 position:16% line:83% align:start
Brother, do you know the
ingredients that make

00:19:26.976 --> 00:19:29.078 position:13% line:89% align:start
this great summer banquet?

00:19:32.248 --> 00:19:35.184 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's a whole mixture of
things, like blueberry bushes

00:19:35.217 --> 00:19:40.490 position:10% line:83% align:start
and trees covered with fruit,
and sunrises over the river,

00:19:40.524 --> 00:19:42.659 position:21% line:83% align:start
and the freckles that
you have on your arms,

00:19:42.692 --> 00:19:46.962 position:13% line:83% align:start
and the moonlight over the
mountains and the starry skies,

00:19:46.996 --> 00:19:50.100 position:7% line:89% align:start
the noonday heat in the woods,

00:19:50.133 --> 00:19:53.537 position:19% line:83% align:start
when the sun is shining
on the great fir trees,

00:19:53.570 --> 00:19:56.006 position:16% line:83% align:start
and the light rain in the
evening, and squirrels

00:19:56.039 --> 00:20:02.245 position:7% line:83% align:start
